Good morning <!channel> ! Since Ewald and I are headed to the airport, let's do a virtual stand-up this morning. On my end: Heading to the airport. Constellation image creation is underway (by Skrillex's friend Sus Boy, above). We should have the first few on the 20th, all final files due on the 25th. Sent image CMS (initial response was good). Sent Overview Deck. Production meeting with the bigger team on Thursday.

wait - not sure what you mean by wallpaper CMS. That's what I was calling "image CMS" (the latest). Got an initial thumbs up and will await any formal feedback

cool! standard emojis as part of the message, right? assuming custom icons still need to be handled as icons, only displayed at the end of the message?
yes about standard emojis. Icons will be placed on the left where the image is or in the small icon location which would be on the lower right of the medium icon shown.
